{"1227690":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Severed Steel","steam_appid":1227690,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"controller_support":"full","dlc":[1754220,1754230],"detailed_description":"<h1>Join Us On Discord<\/h1><p><a href=\"https:\/\/steamcommunity.com\/linkfilter\/?url=https:\/\/discord.gg\/jG8JbEKzJp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  ><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SeveredSteelAd_Discord620x160.png?t=1643058424\" \/><\/a><\/p><br><h1>Severed Steel's Future is Solid:<\/h1><p><a href=\"https:\/\/store.steampowered.com\/news\/app\/1227690\/view\/3052870530040434268\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  ><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SS_Roadmap_headerbanner.png?t=1643058424\" \/><\/a><\/p><br><h1>About the Game<\/h1><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif02.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><br><br>Severed Steel is a single-player FPS featuring a fluid stunt system, destructible voxel environments, loads of bullet time, and a unique one-armed protagonist. It's you, your trigger finger, and a steel-toed boot against a superstructure full of bad guys. Chain together wall runs, dives, flips, and slides to take every last enemy down.<br><br><strong>Key Features<\/strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Unique Fighter<\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif04.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><br><br>Play as Steel, a nimble, one-armed sharpshooter on a mission. There is no reloading – pick your shots well and be ready to pry a loaded weapon from your enemies' cold dead hands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stylish Combat<\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif03.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><br><br>Dodge bullets, leap off walls, slide kick, throw weapons – do whatever it takes to come out on top in intense and frenzied firefights.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fully Destructible Environment<\/h2><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif01.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><br><br>Pepper through plaster with sharp 4.7 mm rounds, punch through thick concrete with .50 cal slugs, or make big holes in things with your arm cannon.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif05.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dynamic AI<\/h2>No two battles are the same thanks to dynamic, unscripted, squad-based AI.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Firefight Mode<\/h2>Chase high scores and fast times for leaderboard acclaim in this arcade-styled mode. Features 42 levels, each with their own sub-challenges, and over 20 unlockable, game modifying 'Mutators'.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Campaign Mode<\/h2>Blast through six compact story chapters as you battle against the forces of nefarious mega-corporation, EdenSys.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Accessibility<\/h2>A range of adjustable settings for features such as difficulty, visuals, audio, controls, navigation, and more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Level Editor (with Steam Workshop support)<\/h2>Build levels and share them with the community. Note: This feature is in beta and will continue to be updated post-launch.","about_the_game":"<img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif02.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><br><br>Severed Steel is a single-player FPS featuring a fluid stunt system, destructible voxel environments, loads of bullet time, and a unique one-armed protagonist. It's you, your trigger finger, and a steel-toed boot against a superstructure full of bad guys. Chain together wall runs, dives, flips, and slides to take every last enemy down.<br><br><strong>Key Features<\/strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Unique Fighter<\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif04.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><br><br>Play as Steel, a nimble, one-armed sharpshooter on a mission. There is no reloading – pick your shots well and be ready to pry a loaded weapon from your enemies' cold dead hands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stylish Combat<\/h2><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif03.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><br><br>Dodge bullets, leap off walls, slide kick, throw weapons – do whatever it takes to come out on top in intense and frenzied firefights.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fully Destructible Environment<\/h2><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif01.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><br><br>Pepper through plaster with sharp 4.7 mm rounds, punch through thick concrete with .50 cal slugs, or make big holes in things with your arm cannon.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1227690\/extras\/SevStee_SteamGif05.gif?t=1643058424\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dynamic AI<\/h2>No two battles are the same thanks to dynamic, unscripted, squad-based AI.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Firefight Mode<\/h2>Chase high scores and fast times for leaderboard acclaim in this arcade-styled mode. Features 42 levels, each with their own sub-challenges, and over 20 unlockable, game modifying 'Mutators'.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Campaign Mode<\/h2>Blast through six compact story chapters as you battle against the forces of nefarious mega-corporation, EdenSys.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Accessibility<\/h2>A range of adjustable settings for features such as difficulty, visuals, audio, controls, navigation, and more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Level Editor (with Steam Workshop support)<\/h2>Build levels and share them with the community. Note: This feature is in beta and will continue to be updated post-launch.","short_description":"A stylish single-player FPS featuring a fluid stunt system, destructible voxel environments, loads of bullet time, a unique one-armed protagonist, and a dark electronic soundtrack.","supported_lan